column1: # Region: northern Baffin Bay & Nares Strait
# Station numbers in the original file were alpha-numeric. Translated to pure numeric via:
# Other: Barium and O-18 data (K.Falkner) included in file
# Header info from previous versions of bottle file
# DELO18 calibrated with Vienna Standard Mean Ocean Water (VSMOW).
# CTDTMP is average of temp1 and temp2.
# CTDSAL is average of Salinities from CTD 1 amd CTD 2; except merged CTDSAL2 only for Casts 39 - 50, CTDSAL 1 missing.
# Station KS01, Cast 45, Bottles 6. Bottle flag 4,         SAMPNO blank in original Excel file, No water samples, deleted
# Station KS09, Cast 48, Bottles 11 & 12.  Bottle flags 9, SAMPNO blank in original Excel file, No water samples, deleted
# Many CFC-11, CFC12 and CCL4 have apparently good values but blank Quality Flags. Used 2 for missing Quality Flag.
# NITRAT is NO2 subracted from NO3+NO2.
# Many values are blank on the Excel file with Quality Flags 9. Added -999 for missing values.
# Station B01, Cast 2, Bottle 24, 12.3db, OXYGEN flag changed from 2 to 9. Missing value blank on Excel file changed to -999.
# All data in volume units converted to mass units using 'convert_per_litre_to_per_kg_exchange.py'.
